### ================================================================
### 完整集成测试 (Gateway :8080 / Auth :8081 / QA Java :8082 / Python :8000)
### ================================================================

### ================================================================
### 前置：建库建表（在 MySQL 中执行）
### ================================================================
### CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS auth_db CHARACTER SET utf8mb4;
### USE auth_db;
### SOURCE auth/src/main/resources/db/init.sql;
###
### CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS smart_km_report_gen CHARACTER SET utf8mb4;
### USE smart_km_report_gen;
### SOURCE qa-chat-service/src/main/resources/db/conversation.sql;
### SOURCE qa-chat-service/src/main/resources/db/model_config.sql;
### SOURCE qa-chat-service/src/main/resources/db/mock_data.sql;

### ================================================================
### 启动服务（4 个终端）
### ================================================================
### 终端1: mvn spring-boot:run -pl auth
### 终端2: mvn spring-boot:run -pl qa-chat-service
### 终端3: $env:PYTHONPATH="qa-agent"; python qa-agent/main.py
### 终端4: mvn spring-boot:run -pl gateway


### ================================================================
### 第三步：验证 Auth (:8081)
### ================================================================

### 1. 注册
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "test01", "password": "123456"}

### 2. 登录（预置账户 admin/admin123）
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "admin", "password": "admin123"}

### 3. 获取当前用户（替换 token）
GET http://localhost:8081/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 刷新 Token
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{"refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"}


### ================================================================
### 第四步：验证 Gateway (:8080)
### ================================================================

### 1. 通过 Gateway 登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "admin", "password": "admin123"}

### 2. 白名单路径（无需 token）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "test02", "password": "123456"}

### 3. 带 token 访问受保护路径
GET http://localhost:8080/api/model-configs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 无 token → 401
GET http://localhost:8080/api/model-configs

### 5. QA 对话（Python :8000 通过 Gateway）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{"conversation_id": {{conversation_id}}, "question": "什么是技术监督？", "user_id": 1}


### ================================================================
### 第五步：模型配置管理
### ================================================================

### 1. 新增 DeepSeek 配置
POST http://localhost:8080/api/model-configs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "provider": "deepseek",
  "baseUrl": "https://api.deepseek.com",
  "modelName": "deepseek-chat",
  "apiKey": "sk-your-deepseek-key",
  "scenario": "chat"
}

### 2. 查看列表（apiKey 脱敏）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/model-configs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 修改配置
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/model-configs/{{config_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "provider": "deepseek",
  "baseUrl": "https://api.deepseek.com",
  "modelName": "deepseek-chat",
  "apiKey": "sk-new-key",
  "scenario": "chat"
}

### 4. 设为默认
POST http://localhost:8080/api/model-configs/{{config_id}}/default
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 删除配置
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/model-configs/{{config_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Python 内部接口（无需 token，直连 :8082）
GET http://localhost:8082/internal/model-configs/default?userId=1&scenario=chat


### ================================================================
### 验证清单
### ================================================================
### [ ] Auth 注册         → 200 或 1002
### [ ] Auth 登录         → 返回 token + userId + username + roles
### [ ] Auth /me          → 返回用户名和角色
### [ ] Auth 刷新         → 返回新 token（旧 token 失效）
### [ ] Gateway 转发登录  → 和直接调 Auth 一样
### [ ] 无 token 访问     → 401 "缺少认证信息"
### [ ] 带 token 访问     → 正常返回
### [ ] 模型配置 CRUD     → 增删改查正常
### [ ] Python 内部接口   → 返回解密 apiKey
